T1  - Time—Path Types: From Static to Dynamic Typologies
AU  - Myers, John G.
AU  - Nicosia, Francesco M.
Y1  - 1970/06/01
PY  - 1970
DA  - 1970/06/01
N1  - doi: 10.1287/mnsc.16.10.B584
